She made headlines earlier this year at the Durban July (SA) due to her skimpy outfits and dance moves. With unkempt natural hair and high heels, Zodwa Wabantu has earned fans across the region including Botswana. She has been vocal about her decision not to wear any unde_rwear, telling South African media ,&#8221;Und_erwear makes me uncomfortable. I don t feel se_xy when I m wearing pan_ties. It s a preference. And people should deal with it.&#8221; The controversial Zodwa was in Gaborone at MKOP (Riverwalk mall) tonight to mingle with her newly found fanbase. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;!